{
  "stem": "13258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told my father that he has to get out of Beuthen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I had to explain that when my father joined the paper, which was in Poland, we were, by the fact that Katowice had become Polish in 1922, Polish citizens, a fact which-- of which, I, in 1932, at first was not aware either.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the paper hired my father, they made as a conditions that he kept the Polish citizenship.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even so, until 1928, he had been entitled to apply to receive the German citizenship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the paper, which was owned by Germans, didn't want it because they were afraid the Poles could kick him out if he is a German citizen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would not allow it-- give him a working permit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we are Polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father is called to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they tell him, get out from here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father immediately packed some stuff because he was afraid they were going to arrest him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But before that happened, my still-- parents were called to the school and were told that I wouldn't be allowed to finish the school year-- which in Germany at that time ended in April-- and that the next year, I would not be allowed to enroll anymore.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even so, that principal of the school was a personal friend of my parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave them to understand that that was not his doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could not say so outright.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Apparently, he was afraid already that somebody might be listening in or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was the situation as it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so my father immediately rented a room with a family-- furnished room and stayed in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
